Citation
--------
If you use the dataset or map in research or journalism, please cite:

  No Pressure Lab. Aragón Datacenter Map.
  https://github.com/nopressurelab/dc-map

Sources
-------
Every datapoint in `data/datacenters.json` is cited inline. The dataset is a
secondary compilation; the original facts are owned by their respective sources
(BOA, BOE, INAGA, CHE, Heraldo de Aragón, El País, Reuters, Datacenter
Dynamics, and others linked in each record). The compilation, structure, and
editorial choices are licensed CC BY 4.0.
